comment: What the actual fuck?I'm pretty sure there are way worse diseases we should be concerned about than Coronavirus. You know, like the flu. What if this coronavirus was an issue in Europe and this was a European event? Would they really cancel it then?  https://t.co/zAJPdA4mF9
@Terra_Forever I think I know what is going on. I read a few news articles that some people are literally "hiding" that they have the coronavirus instead of getting treated.
